    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight pb-4">About</h1>

    <p class="text-md font-light mb-4 mt-1">
      Coulsy Joinery is a family-owned carpentry and joinery business, founded
      and operated by myself, Robert, a professional joiner with over three
      decades of experience. Since qualifying with distinction in 1988, Iâ€™ve
      dedicated myself to mastering my craft, and I now specialise in the repair
      and maintenance of fire doors. This extensive background allows me to
      bring exceptional skill and attention to detail to every fire door
      project, ensuring that they meet the highest safety and quality standards.
    </p>
    <p class="text-md font-light mb-4 mt-1">
      We provide top-tier carpentry services, including fire door repairs,
      inspections, and compliance work, in addition to small build works,
      alterations, and building maintenance.
    </p>

    <p class="text-md font-light mb-4 mt-1">
      Working alongside me is my wife, Debbie, whose dedication is vital to our
      success. Together, we lead a trusted team of skilled professionals who
      share our commitment to quality, customer satisfaction, and safety. Our
      hands-on approach ensures that each fire door repair project is completed
      with precision, tailoring our services to meet specific client
      requirements and ensuring compliance with fire safety regulations.
    </p>

